Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím... Prosím...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:08.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som za to zodpovedný.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:11.57,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Potrestajte len mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj ľud o ničom nevedeľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:26.68,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechám vás ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.58,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš ísť a žiť, kým nezomrieš na starobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:34.59,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím o milosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:37.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, zľutujte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.17,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I let my childhood dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.38,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Flow freely out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:53.18,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,In scribbles that don't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:58.75,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,And they connect to the future I conceive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:04.35,Utawarerumono2,,0000,0000,0000,,Utawarerumono
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:10.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,The clear sky, endlessly blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:17.50,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Captivates me, my heart is filled with innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:21.78,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll soon gain wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:24.71,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,That will let me fly freely about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:29.42,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,My innocent eyes go on searching
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:33.05,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go beyond the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:36.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all my endless wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:39.69,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,If only one of them comes true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:43.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to give it up to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:47.34,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to grasp my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,My childhood dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:54.01,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever continued to be drawn out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:57.68,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,In scribbles that don't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:03.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,They connect to a future I wish for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:18.80,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kráľovská pečať
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.83,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže, Elemui padli...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:33.35,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.82,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Gachatara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.06,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si urobila takú vec?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.03,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takú vec?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.37,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápeš, čo sa ťa pýtam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.76,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si zničila Elemui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.34,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, takže to je o tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:07.82,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Tí ľudia už nemali silu bojovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.94,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že som ti povedala, aby si sa \Nneobťažovala s tými, ktorí sa nebránia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:14.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,"Keď na nich pôjdeme zľahka, budú nami len pohŕdať."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:16.82,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepovedali ste to Vy, Vaša Výsosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:21.22,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,A preto si vyvraždila celý klan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:25.76,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne, urobila som to v záujme Vášho Veličenstva.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Hauenkua!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.17,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takéto chovanie si k Jej Veličenstvu vyprosujeme!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.54,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je cesta, ktorou sa prihováram k ľuďom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.18,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že si to uvedomujete, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:38.94,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre všetko... Lord Hien, prosím povedzte niečo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.62,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Hien?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.74,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, Vaša Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.56,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hauenkua, počula som tvoje vysvetlenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.63,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ani je nie som úplne čistá.\NŤiež som urobila chybu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.46,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nateraz ťa nechám ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Cením si vašu šlachetnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaša Výsosť, dovolťe mi prosím hovoriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.87,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,O čo ide, Hien?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:07.48,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebolo by teraz vhodné, upevniť vašu\N pozíciu zjednotením krajín?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.77,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Spojenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:14.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Za týchto okolností, nemôžem povedať, kedy sa znova objaví nepriateľ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.75,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je najväčší dôvod, prečo by sme mali spojiť naše krajiny
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:21.19,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,a nastoliť pravý mier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.83,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš, že občas hovoríš rozumné veci!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:28.76,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, mali by sme ukázať svetu, ktorý klan\N by mal vládnuť celému svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:32.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Naším zámerom je aliancia, nie nadvláda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.50,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo, nie sú to v podstate rovnaké veci?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci sa spoja pod vládou Shakukopolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:41.34,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjednotenie ľudí a vládnutie ľuďom\N sú dve rozdielne veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.45,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjednostenie a vládnutie je tá istá vec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.81,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýliš sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.11,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemýlim sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.08,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hauenkua...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.75,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kčertu s...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.65,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Utíšte sa! Stojíte pred Jej Veličenstvom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.32,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Genjimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:04.96,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si o tom myslíš, Genjimaru?\NMám zjednotiť krajiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:13.10,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Radšej ako rozšíriť naše územie, verím, že\N musíme posilniť vlastnú krajinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.14,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš tým povedať, že s mojou krajinou\N nie je všetko v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.81,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne to tým chcem povedať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:23.64,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem. Počúvnem tvoju radu, Genjimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.59,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,V prvom rade posilníme našu krajinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, Vaša Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.65,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš, kde je tvoje miesto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:33.32,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si nepočul slová Jej Výsosti?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpustite mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:49.03,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pane, čo takto pre zmenu\N robiť mi spoločnosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zobrala som zopár šálok čaju spolu so sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.51,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, ale musím ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Vaša Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.47,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Bratre!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.54,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcete ísť von? Budem vám robiť doprovod.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.31,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, prosím pokračujte.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte, že som vás vyrušil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.91,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďalší!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.05,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďalší!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.52,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.85,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Eruruu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.12,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dajte do toho trochu odhodlania!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:44.49,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Som šťastný, keď vidím, akých\N skvelých ľudí mám okolo seba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.00,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám správu, Pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:54.66,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nunbani a Happrap napadli Kunekamun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:56.48,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:07:01.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Po tom čo sa stalo s Nosecheskou,\Nmala byť sila Kunekamunu jasná.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.97,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Podľa všetkého si mysleli, že spojením síl budú mať šancu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.52,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako pokračujú boje?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.68,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunekamun mal jasnú prevahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:18.55,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto sa stene tím, ktorí napadnú Kunekamun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:33.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takto vyzerá vojna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.24,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte mi, že hovorím...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:43.36,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sme takto prenasledovaní?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.42,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Keby ste chceli, mohli ste si podrobiť celú krajinu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosíme o milosť z tohto chaosu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:53.66,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,len pár dní bez strachu, že nás napadne ďalší klan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľmi dobre chápem, ako sa cítite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.80,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz ale musíme upevniť naše hranice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je naj...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.51,Utawarerumono3,,0000,0000,0000,,Kedy to už bude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:06.14,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To máme byť zabíjaní, až kým nás nevyvraždia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.82,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo myslíte tým posíliť?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.69,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráti mi toto "posílenie" moje deti, ktoré boli dnes zabité?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:21.26,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,My sme ľud vybraní naším otcom, Onvitaikayanom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:27.69,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, ukážte všetkým silu Kunekamunu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiadame vás!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.87,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiadame vás!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.74,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže boje znovu začali?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.45,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.62,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Avšak je pravda, že v Kunekamunu boli
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:45.62,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,nejaké hlasy, ktoré vystúpili v prospech ovládnutia všetkých krajín.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:49.56,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čokoľvek sa stane, je asi najlepšie byť pripravený.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.99,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dúfam, že sa to nakoniec ukáže byť nepotrebné.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.06,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňte ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prednešok stačilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:19.11,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslíš si, že je dnes v noci mesiac prekrásny, Hakuoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.58,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesiac?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.16,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Rada sa pozerám na mesiac,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:33.00,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,pretože nežiari tak silno ako slnko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:38.91,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesačný svit žiari v tme a zahaluje nás vo svojom jemnom svetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:43.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorí sa, že Onvitaikayan miluje mesiac viac ako denné slnko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.85,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.32,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak o tom nechceš hovoriť, nebudem ťa tlačiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.62,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:05.17,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíš držať všetky problémy v sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdo nie je dokonalý.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.37,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Každý trpí z problémov a zranení,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:15.47,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,a myslím, že všetci si prajú mať \Nniekoho, o koho sa môžu oprieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.14,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Si taký tiež, Hakuoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Samozrejme.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš tým Eruruu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.89,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, presne tak.\NMám Eruruu a ostatných.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:33.49,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,A Kuuya, ty máš Genjimarua a Sakuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.70,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak máš problémy, zver sa im.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.87,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie som sama, ja som?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.08,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaútočíme na ďalšiu dedinu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.81,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nasledujte ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebatsue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:19.07,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem, že chcete upevniť svoju vlastnú krajinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.53,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale táto situácia nám to ďalej neumožňuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:28.91,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zatiaľ, čo my sme tu, naši ľudia na hraniciach trpia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.62,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je už teraz čas, aby ste sa rozhodli?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:37.92,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci chcú aby ste zjednotili krajiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:41.26,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak všetko čo robíme je len naša ochrana,\Npotom nemôžeme zachrániť náš ľud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:44.30,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,V snahe vybudovať svet, v ktorom\N budeme žiť bez starostí,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.49,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,nemáme inú možnosť len povstať!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:50.40,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,A hlavne, mi máme silu dokázať to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,My máme Avu Kamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.47,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je Genjimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:01.62,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vzal Sakuyu na kontrolu vesníc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.85,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám správu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:12.95,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebatsue-ovia postupujú rýchlo, dedina Sankukattaru\Nbola vypálená do tla!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:14.96,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaša Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:19.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zachráni "posílenie" tých, čo boli dnes zabití?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.53,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:32.04,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja... Ja už nemôžem prehliadať vaše argumenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.61,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Počúvajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.62,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozhodla som sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozneste toto posolstvo po celej krajine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:49.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja, Kuuya Amrulineulka, zjednotím celú zem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:50.93,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, Vaša Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.54,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunekamun je vo vojne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.98,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.08,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zpevni našu obranu na severe, Touka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.38,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.05,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem s tebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.05,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Skapte!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:40.04,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci skapte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.60,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Výsosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.06,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Onkamiyamukai-ovia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:30.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Onkamiyamukai-ovia nie sú nič, len pokorní\N ľudia uctievajúci Boha nešťastia .
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:35.86,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Skôr alebo neskôr budeme proti nim bojovať,\Npodľa mňa by bolo lepšie skôr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.91,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.45,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Witsalnemitea je pre nich hlavnou oporou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:49.88,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak zaútočíte na Onkamiyamukai-ov,\Npoštvete si všetkých proti sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.45,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj chcete oddeliť seba od ostatných?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:57.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Genjimaru, my už sme oddelený.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:05.40,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdo na tomto svete by sa nespojil s Shakukopolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.53,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hien, Hauenkua...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.34,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Pani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.47,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Zajtra skoro ráno vyrážame. Pripravte sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, Vaša Výsosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:16.04,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo ste už zabudli na láskavosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.55,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takto ju všetku zanecháte.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.11,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,V tom prípade...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa jej zmocním znova.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:32.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíte si, že sa jej môžete zmocniť silou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.62,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Starý otec...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:38.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Už sa to nedá zastaviť\Nkeď bol vydaný rozkaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.56,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Sestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:48.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to pravda, že Kunekamun napadol otcovu krajinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.68,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Neboj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.74,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Otec bude v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:05.85,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké smutné, že majú byť vydaní takému osudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.94,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.96,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.25,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kráľovská pečať!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.71,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže toto je ich tronf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:04.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakukopolu, ty, ktorý si obľúbencom Onvitaikayana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.75,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,a ty, kto si bol prenasledovaný pre svoju oddanosť,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:14.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,môžeš teraz odpočivať v pokoji v ruách nášho boha, Witsalnemitea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.01,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaša Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.08,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Som v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.88,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:44.86,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:47.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kráľovská pečať!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.46,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kdo si?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.97,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dii... Ty žiješ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.57,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemožné, ty si...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:06.01,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, to nie je možné,\Nani ty by si to neurobil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.81,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadišiel čas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.25,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadišiel čas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.71,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?! To nemôže byť! Ty si...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.70,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Získali sme kontrolu nad Onkamiyamukaimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.43,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Výborne, teraz, potom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hauenkua!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Výsosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:33.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Priveďte Hakuora, kráľa Tuskuru ku mne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.67,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Výborne, Vaša Výsosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.31,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Onkamiyamukai-ovia padli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.45,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáme žiadne správy o najvyššom kňazovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.92,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Sastra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.61,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Otec je... Otec je...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:49.22,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Munto, zvolaj Ajari.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.02,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, Moja pani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:55.00,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Camus, Otec určite žije.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz tomu musíme veriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.20,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:03.16,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíme urobiť to, čo je potrebné, v otcovom mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.63,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomôžeš mi, Camus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.63,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomôžem ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.28,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prinášame správy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:14.75,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunekamun prekročil naše hranice a mieri do Tuskuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:18.34,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Hrad Houhoro padol. Posádka hradu bola zmasakrovaná.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.79,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo s Toukou a Kurou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:30.59,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Udržujú nepriateľa v tiesni, zatiaľ čo ustupujú k nám.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Oboro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:36.50,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Poznáš silu Kunekamunu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.51,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa pustíme do boja, stratíme len viac ľudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.97,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, Bratre!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:43.53,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Opustíme hlavné mesto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.98,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vzhľadom na súčasnú situáciu,\Nje to najlepšia voľba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:55.65,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Eruruu, nech civilné obyvateľstvo opustí mesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:56.96,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo bude s tebou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:02.10,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,My budeme zdržovať nepriateľa, kým sa neskončí evakuácia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.29,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, musíte odísť s ostatnými, Pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.07,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Benawi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:09.47,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni chcú vás.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.47,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:16.64,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Kým budete v bezpečí, máme stále nádej.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.95,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, nechajte to na nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:26.18,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, skúste porozumieť pocitom vašich poddaných.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:29.85,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.39,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale toto nie je koniec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.52,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci, musíte prežiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.37,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to ksakru je?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.21,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,To je sila Kunekamunu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.77,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to tak, že sa konečne zabavím.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.92,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Tuskuru je nie je nič iné, len banda hlupákov.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.38,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:07.52,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Si myslíte, že zastavíte Avu Kamu s\Nvašimi hrdzavými mečmi a tupými šípmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:15.24,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Našou úlohou je získať čas na dokončenie evakuácie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:17.90,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Nekonaj ľahkomyselne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.37,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja to viem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.51,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže poďme...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:42.23,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst solitude where even flame has frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:49.27,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I seek this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:57.81,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Join your soul to mine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:06.22,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,And warm me with your love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:14.45,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my words of prayer quiver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:22.13,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, even if my fragile life is extinguished
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:30.41,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow the flow of the repeating\Ncycles of incarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:38.72,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazing upon the destiny of an endless world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:46.33,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,You, whose song is sung and sung again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:55.26,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,This evening you doze off, protected...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:23:06.00,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Preložil: Gurthfin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:12.01,Utawarerumono,,0000,0000,0000,,Odius Pact
